Classes in org.cougaar.planning.ldm.policy that implement RuleParameter
 class BooleanRuleParameter
          A BooleanRuleParameter is a RuleParameter that contains a single true or false value
 class ClassRuleParameter
          A ClassRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with specified/protected Java interface/class that returns an Class that implements that interface or extends that class
 class DoubleRuleParameter
          An DoubleRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with specified/protected double bounds that returns a Double
 class EnumerationRuleParameter
          An EnumerationRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with specified/protected string selections that returns a string
 class IntegerRuleParameter
          An IntegerRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with specified/protected integer bounds that returns an Integer
 class KeyRuleParameter
          An KeyRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with a list of key/value pairs and a default value.
 class LongRuleParameter
          An LongRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with specified/protected long bounds that returns an Long
 class PredicateRuleParameter
          An PredicateRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with a UnaryPredicate as its value.
 class RangeRuleParameter
          An RangeRuleParameter is a RuleParameter with a list of integer-range delineated values and a default value.
 class StringRuleParameter
          An StringRuleParameter is a RuleParameter that returns an arbitrary string
